Gotta be small anthros for modern warfare. It's mostly mechanised so you want smaller crewmen for your vehicles and the lethality of modern small arms vs the inadequacy of body armour means being smaller, faster, quieter and generally harder to hit trumps everything else for infantry. You also want something with natural night vision because NODs are fucking expensive and night fighting capability is a requirement for modern infantry.

Anon, I want this to not demotivate you more, but your expectations are perhaps out of line with reality. Art is not something that just magically happens, most good artists I know have been drawing for years and years. Now, it doesn’t take that long to get to silly little ms paint doodles, but you will not be magically picking it up instantly. If it’s something you want to pursue. Consider a longer-term plan, and do consistent practice even if it’s something simple like practicing lines and shapes. I strongly believe that anyone can draw, but it’s about discipline rather than talent.
